to Find</a></li><li><a href="/pubmedhealth/n/ucalpkyc/CH4/#S18">Questions to Ask about Risk Reduction</a></li></ul></li><li><a href="/pubmedhealth/n/ucalpkyc/CH5/">Chapter 5. Not All Benefits Are Equal: Understand the Outcome</a><ul class="simple-list toc bktoc_lst_exp"><li><a href="/pubmedhealth/n/ucalpkyc/CH5/#S19">Better Test Results</a></li><li><a href="/pubmedhealth/n/ucalpkyc/CH5/#S21">Fewer Symptoms of Disease</a></li><li><a href="/pubmedhealth/n/ucalpkyc/CH5/#S23">Fewer Deaths from Disease</a></li></ul></li></ul></li><li><a href="/pubmedhealth/n/ucalpkyc/PART3/">Part 3. Does Risk Reduction Have Downsides?</a><ul class="simple-list toc bktoc_lst_exp"><li><a href="/pubmedhealth/n/ucalpkyc/CH6/">Chapter 6. Consider the Downsides</a></li><li><a href="/pubmedhealth/n/ucalpkyc/CH7/">Chapter 7. Do the Benefits Outweigh the Downsides?</a><ul class="simple-list toc bktoc_lst_exp"><li><a href="/pubmedhealth/n/ucalpkyc/CH7/#S25">An Important Bottom Line: Death from All Causes Combined</a></li><li><a href="/pubmedhealth/n/ucalpkyc/CH7/#S26">Making Decisions</a></li></ul></li></ul></li><li><a href="/pubmedhealth/n/ucalpkyc/PART4/">Part 4. Developing a Healthy Skepticism</a><ul class="simple-list toc bktoc_lst_exp"><li><a href="/pubmedhealth/n/ucalpkyc/CH8/">Chapter 8. Beware of Exaggerated Importance</a><ul class="simple-list toc bktoc_lst_exp"><li><a href="/pubmedhealth/n/ucalpkyc/CH8/#S27">A Special Case of Exaggerated Numbers: Survival Statistics</a></li></ul></li><li><a href="/pubmedhealth/n/ucalpkyc/CH9/">Chapter 9. Beware of Exaggerated Certainty</a><ul class="simple-list toc bktoc_lst_exp"><li><a href="/pubmedhealth/n/ucalpkyc/CH9/#S30">What Kind of Science Is Behind the Numbers?</a></li><li><a href="/pubmedhealth/n/ucalpkyc/CH9/#S32">Is It Too Early?</a></li></ul></li><li><a href="/pubmedhealth/n/ucalpkyc/CH10/">Chapter 10. Whoâ€™s Behind the Numbers?</a></li></ul></li><li><a href="/pubmedhealth/n/ucalpkyc/AG1/">Extra Help</a><ul class="simple-list toc bktoc_lst_exp"><li><a href="/pubmedhealth/n/ucalpkyc/APP1/">Quick Summary</a></li><li><a href="/pubmedhealth/n/ucalpkyc/APP2/">Glossary</a></li><li><a href="/pubmedhealth/n/ucalpkyc/APP3/">Number Converter and Risk Charts</a></li><li><a href="/pubmedhealth/n/ucalpkyc/APP4/">Credible Sources of Health Statistics</a></li></ul></li><li><a href="/pubmedhealth/n/ucalpkyc/RL1/">NOTES</a></li></ul></div><span class="glossary-control"><glossary-control id="toggle-glossary-link-bottom" ref="pagearea=nav&amp;targetsite=control&amp;targetcat=control"><a href="#" class="toggle-glossary-link" title="Enable/disable links to the glossary">Disable Glossary Links</a></glossary-control></span><div class="pagination"><a class="active page_link prev" href="/pubmedhealth/n/ucalpkyc/toc/" ref="nav&amp;targetsite=bookshelf&amp;targetcat=book-part">&lt; Prev</a><a class="active page_link next" href="/pubmedhealth/n/ucalpkyc/PART1/" ref="nav&amp;targetsite=bookshelf&amp;targetcat=book-part">Next &gt;</a></div></div>
